mosquitto (1.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Upstream license has changed from BSD to dual EPL/EDL.
  * Port to multiarch.
  * Add new package mosquitto-dev for plugin development.
  * Split debug package for multi-arch.
  * Bump standards verson to 3.9.6. No changes needed.
  * Remove mosquitto-python package, no longer provided by upstream.

 -- Roger A. Light <roger@atchoo.org>  Thu, 04 Jun 2015 22:31:19 +0100

